OL,5,ERussty Russ goes all russty on teletext
OL,7,BCue the scene... it's probablyE1984Band
OL,8,Bmy parents are visiting friends in     
OL,9,BLondon and their lady friend shows me  
OL,10,Bteletext for the first time in my life 
OL,11,BandEI'm in awe.                        
OL,13,BPretty sure I was just pagingEOracle   
OL,14,Bthat night but the computerised text   
OL,15,BjustEmesmerised me.                    
OL,17,BThat evening was short lived but come  
OL,18,B1988, my parents rented a teletext set 
OL,19,Bfor us to enjoy.                       
