OL,5,EIt was all about Barney's Bunch        
OL,7,BSaturday mornings would see me page the
OL,8,Bupdated weeklyEFun and GamesBsection on
OL,9,BBBC2 just before turning over to watch 
OL,10,EGoing Live!Bfor the next three hours.  
OL,12,BOther memories include paging theEWorld
OL,13,EClockBsponsored by British Airways,    
OL,14,EBarney's Bunch,Band catching up on the 
OL,15,BTop 40.                                
OL,17,BI was the one that would be glued to   
OL,18,Bthe page numbers rolling around to see 
OL,19,Bany out of sync with the rest.         
