OL,5,EORACLE is about to end                 
OL,7,BThe anorak in me would seeErandom test 
OL,8,EpagesBwhich of course we weren't meant 
OL,9,Bto see but I did.                      
OL,11,BMy parents would give back the rented  
OL,12,Bset inE1989Bbut I would pester them a  
OL,13,Blot to get me one for my bedroom.      
OL,15,BEventually they caved inEMarch 1992Bbut
OL,16,Bthe fun was short lived as Oracle      
OL,17,Bannounced their licenceEwould be ending
OL,18,Blater that year.                       
