OL,5,EDebbie's Diary and ORACLE RIP          
OL,7,BAs the months went by in 1992, I would 
OL,8,Bbe readingEDebbie's DiaryBon Buzz! and 
OL,9,Bcatching up on 4-Tel'sE4-T.            
OL,11,BCome New Years Eve 1992 which saw      
OL,12,EOracle's final night,Bit would be a sad
OL,13,Bsight seeing Oracle bowing out.        
OL,15,BFortunatelyEteletext wizardsBin the    
OL,16,B21st century with their recoveries have
OL,17,Bbrought it back to watch it bow out    
OL,18,Bagain and again.                       
