OL,5,ETeletext.. the soft spot in my heart   
OL,7,BTeletext (as in the medium) has always 
OL,8,Bhad a soft spot in my heart. It played 
OL,9,Ba part inEmy childhoodBand stuck with  
OL,10,Bme every day.                          
OL,12,BIt's aEbeautiful mediumBwhich I will   
OL,13,Balways praise and champion and it is   
OL,14,Bstill very muchEalive todayBthrough    
OL,15,Brecoveries, artwork, and much more.    
OL,17,BThe medium of teletext has aEwonderful 
OL,18,EcommunityBof dedicated people.         
