OL,5,EMaking every character count           
OL,7,BFinally if there's one thing I was     
OL,8,Bimpressed by on teletext, it's those   
OL,9,Bwho couldEfill every lineBof text from 
OL,10,Bone end to another especially on the   
OL,11,Enews headlineBpages.                   
OL,13,BClearly, I couldn't master that here   
OL,14,BbutEhere's to teletextB50+ years going.
OL,16,BAll the best "teletext-ers"            
